name: Renne (Sen no Kiseki + Kuro no Kiseki) LoRA
description:
Renne from Sen no Kiseki IV/Trails of Cold Steel IV and Kuro no Kiseki. Trained on NAI.

Tested at 0.8-1.0 strength.

Contains her Sen IV/CS4 and Kuro I appearances.

  • Trigger word is "renne_sen" for her Sen/CS4 appearance. Add "hair ribbon, black jacket, purple shirt, short sleeves, white skirt, thigh band, cross-laced boots" for her typical look.

  • Trigger word is "renne_kuro" for her Kuro appearance. Add "hair ribbon, green jacket, blue necktie, white shirt, black skirt, black pantyhose, cross-laced boots" for her typical look.
